room_title: Escape room "Room 13" by Breakout CoMo in Columbia (MO)
room_description: You have no recollection of checking in. Mysteriously, you can’t leave. As panic sets in, the hotel’s cozy façade begins to crumble, and the sinister motive lurking behind your imprisonment is unmasked. Embedded in the cracks between past and present, voices guide you to freedom.
